------------- STORYBOARD --------------

Email-based "add to the scene" games
An image board for cool kids
http://storybored.org/howto

Usage:

- start a new game
- N threads will be generated for N players
- each player adds an image or text to the previous text or image (respectively)
- in the end you have a story!


--------------- ABOUT -----------------

100% open source software
Ruby, Merb & ActiveRecord

Built by Jamie Wilkinson <http://jamiedubs.com>
Game design by Bennett Williamson <http://codeblooded.net>

Free Art & Technology Lab <http://fffff.at>
